{"tid":2159244,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中共重刊習舊講話：拒融入西方經濟","createTime":"2020-08-16T08:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T08:43:32.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4338c78c4f3bf6820ee283566f8ef454a8a98de6","tid":2159244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:05:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200816/D6G5HWX7EJFY5AWZXNRX7NQ6QM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200816%2FD6G5HWX7EJFY5AWZXNRX7NQ6QM%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=5a95ee60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200816%2FD6G5HWX7EJFY5AWZXNRX7NQ6QM%2F&h=af25d7f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200816/D6G5HWX7EJFY5AWZXNRX7NQ6QM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n中共重刊習舊講話：拒融入西方經濟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/u1rYCha_hsHsJjSoL-i4Fv2smjM=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJNXEMM6YFDTTAQQJ46W6S67LI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fu1rYCha_hsHsJjSoL-i4Fv2smjM%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJNXEMM6YFDTTAQQJ46W6S67LI.jpg&h=b399ced4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■習近平強調要不斷研究「馬克思主義政治經濟學」。<br />\n<br />\n中共《求是》雜誌刊出總書記習近平五年前在政治局集體學習的講話，重申「國有經濟主導作用不能動搖」，又強調中國的經濟學教學「不能食洋不化」。有分析認為，黨刊此時發表習的舊講話全文，表明習要捍衞其領導地位和執政路線，並向外界表明中國經濟不會融入西方主導的經濟體系。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：王毅罕有赴藏 莫迪強硬衞邊境<br />\n<br />\n於2015年11月23日，政治局就「馬克思主義政治經濟學基本原理和方法論」舉行集體學習，習近平在會上發表講話。最新一期。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n強調「不能食洋不化」<br />\n<br />\n文章指，中國要鞏固和發展公有制經濟，毫不動搖鼓勵、支持、引導非公有制經濟發展，但基本經濟制度是「公有制主體地位不能。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n清華大學政治學前講師吳強向本報表示，習近平過去幾年已不斷。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「翻炒」舊文鞏固習權<br />\n<br />\n「我相信包括中宣部這時候把習近平五年前的文章重新拿出來，從政治經濟學的角度來談，主要是對他自身權力地位不鞏固，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n時事評論員林和立指，《求是》「翻炒」舊講話與中共將在10月舉行五中全會。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"fd337f51d87c594d23b632890661b454ec8a4eb9","tid":2159244,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:15:23.000Z","msg":"加速好"},{"pid":"30385b019ac3a0d7f4255344fe7c670279498c1d","tid":2159244,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:20:13.000Z","msg":"咁咪鎖國lor<br />\n又要不脫勾"},{"pid":"b343255d9be82d85a8fbf6064602f5288772e274","tid":2159244,"uid":31841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:29:57.000Z","msg":"真係咁似晚清<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da52acdf96f0afbdc95f883bb370562069c9a13","tid":2159244,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:35:39.000Z","msg":"咁你唔好抽人水啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85385016d0553a27c24292c4ac14eb35bfa8057d","tid":2159244,"uid":111322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:37:20.000Z","msg":"方向變了！快修正！"},{"pid":"86b2e1af757adab6a8cd5dc596074907281a6516","tid":2159244,"uid":18024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T08:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}